Michele Greene https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michele_Greene 0 Michele Dominguez Greene (born February 13, 1962, in Las Vegas, Nevada) is an American actress, singer/songwriter and author. She is known for her role as attorney Abigail "Abby" Perkins on the TV series L.A. Law from 1986 to 1991 (and reprised the role in the 2002 TV reunion film L.A. Law: The Movie).
